## Coding Style
- Pragmatic, no over-engineering, minimal comments
- Single store (`FleetStore`) injected via `.environment(store)`
- `nonisolated init()` so `@State private var store = FleetStore()` works in `@main`
- All data as `Codable` structs ‚Äî never `[String: Any]`
- Field names stay snake_case on models (match web `Project` TS type for future Supabase decode)

